  "prompt": "What are some good real estate agencies in ahmedabad?",
  "response": "Here are some well-known real estate agencies in Ahmedabad:\n\n1. **Anand Rathi Real Estate** - A reputable agency offering a variety of real estate services, including residential and commercial properties.\n\n2. **Square Yards** - A prominent player in the real estate market, Square Yards provides a comprehensive platform for buyers and sellers.\n\n3. **PropTiger** - Known for its extensive listings and services, PropTiger helps users find new homes, resale properties, and rental options.\n\n4. **Vascon Engineers** - Besides being a construction company, they also deal in real estate development and have a good reputation in the market.\n\n5. **Godrej Properties** - Part of the well-known Godrej Group, they offer a range of residential projects in Ahmedabad.\n\n6. **Kumar Properties** - A reliable agency specializing in residential and commercial properties, providing excellent customer service.\n\n7. **Realty Plus** - Focused on various aspects of real estate, including marketing and consulting, with a solid local presence.\n\n8. **Indiabulls Real Estate** - A well-established name in the real estate sector, offering a variety of projects in the region.\n\n9. **Makaan.com** - An online property portal that connects buyers and sellers, offering a wide range of listings.\n\n10. **Siddhivinayak Real Estate** - Known for local expertise, they offer services tailored to the Ahmedabad market.\n\nBefore choosing an agency, it's advisable to conduct your own research, read reviews, and possibly consult with previous clients to find the agency that best fits your needs.",
